<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٣٠٤ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ عَطَاءً فَقُلْتُ لَهُ: الْغُسْلُ يَوْمَ الْجُمُعَةِ وَاجِبٌ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَعَمْ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>